---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import InfoBox from '../components/InfoBox.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Return & Refund Policy | Montessa Kennel"
  description="Our return and refund policy for our puppies at Montessa Kennel."
  keywords="puppy return policy, refund policy, breeder policy"
>
  <PageHeader
    title="Return & Refund Policy"
    subtitle="Understanding our policies for your peace of mind"
  />

  <section class="info-content">
    <div class="content-container">
      <h2>Our Return & Refund Policy</h2>
      <p>We want every puppy to find their forever home. However, we understand that sometimes circumstances change. Here's our policy to ensure fair treatment for both families and puppies.</p>

      <InfoBox type="info" title="Our Commitment">
        <p>We never want a puppy to end up in a shelter. If you can no longer care for your puppy at any point in their life, please contact us first. We will help find them a loving new home.</p>
      </InfoBox>

      <h3>Deposits</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>A deposit is required to reserve a puppy</li>
        <li>Deposits are non-refundable but can be transferred to another puppy</li>
        <li>If we are unable to provide your reserved puppy, your deposit will be fully refunded or transferred</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Returns Within 72 Hours</h3>
      <p>If you need to return your puppy within 72 hours of pickup/delivery:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Puppy must be returned in the same health condition</li>
        <li>A partial refund may be issued minus the deposit and any delivery fees</li>
        <li>Must provide veterinary records from your vet visit</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Health-Related Returns</h3>
      <p>If your puppy is diagnosed with a genetic health condition covered by our guarantee:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact us immediately with veterinary documentation</li>
        <li>We will work with you to find the best solution</li>
        <li>Options include replacement puppy, partial refund, or veterinary cost assistance</li>
      </ul>

      <InfoBox type="warning" title="Not Covered">
        <ul>
          <li>Health issues caused by accidents, neglect, or improper care</li>
          <li>Conditions resulting from failure to continue vaccinations</li>
          <li>Issues arising from feeding inappropriate food</li>
          <li>Behavioral issues (we're happy to provide training guidance)</li>
        </ul>
      </InfoBox>

      <h3>Rehoming Assistance</h3>
      <p>If at any point you can no longer keep your puppy, please reach out to us. We offer:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Help finding a suitable new home</li>
        <li>Listing assistance on our network</li>
        <li>Guidance through the rehoming process</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Contact Us</h3>
      <p>For any return, refund, or rehoming inquiries, please contact us directly. We handle each situation individually and work to find the best outcome for everyone involved, especially the puppy.</p>

      <div class="cta-box">
        <h3>Have Questions?</h3>
        <p>We're here to help you understand our policies.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .info-content {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .content-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2a2a2a;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f19645;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #5a5a5a;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    color: #5a5a5a;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .cta-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f19645, #e08839);
    color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .cta-box h3 {
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-box p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #e08839;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    background: #d63c3c;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .info-content {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
